Authentication: username-password
Comments: logged in users must be able to write comments
Delete comments: logged users must be able to delete their own comments
Registration: users must be able to register to the site
XML: all recipes should be stored into XML files following the format specified

Input filtering
Password encryption
Cross-site scripting

Database: users (id INT, username VARCHAR(12), password CHAR(128))
Database: comments (username VARCHAR(12), recipeId INT, comment VARCHAR(300))
